Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Diet, Longevity and a Custard Pie
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00szs84
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 2 Jun 2000
Alistair Cooke reflects on the beginning of the national obsession with cholesterol and the scientific study which proved eating too much meat is bad for you.